{"word":"Gath","slug":"gath","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Gath</b> <a href=\"#/H1661\">H1661</a> <br/> One of the five chief cities of the Philistines<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=13&verse=3'>Jos 13:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=6&verse=17'>1Sa 6:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=6&verse=2'>Amo 6:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=33&chapter=1&verse=10'>Mic 1:10</a><br/> Anakim, a race of giants, inhabitants of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=11&verse=22'>Jos 11:22</a><br/> Goliath dwelt in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=17&verse=4'>1Sa 17:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=20&verse=8'>1Ch 20:8</a><br/> Obed-Edom belonged to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=6&verse=10'>2Sa 6:10</a><br/> The ark taken to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=5&verse=8'>1Sa 5:8</a><br/> Inhabitants of, called Gittites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=13&verse=3'>Jos 13:3</a><br/> David takes refuge at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=21&verse=15'>1Sa 21:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=27&verse=7'>1Sa 27:7</a><br/> Band of Gittites, attached to David<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=15&verse=22'>2Sa 15:22</a><br/> Taken by David<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=18&verse=1'>1Ch 18:1</a><br/> Shimei's servants escape to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=2&verse=41'>1Ki 2:41</a><br/> Fortified by Rehoboam<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=11&verse=8'>2Ch 11:8</a><br/> Taken by Hazael<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=12&verse=17'>2Ki 12:17</a><br/> Recovered, by Jehoash<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=13&verse=25'>2Ki 13:25</a><br/> Besieged, by Uzziah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=26&verse=6'>2Ch 26:6</a><br/> Called Metheg-Ammah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=8&verse=1'>2Sa 8:1</a>"}]}